Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:11.32,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1600,1600)\an8\fs32\bord0\c&HA5535A&}Sign: Rumors about Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, Yano was going out with a girl two grades above him...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.14,0:00:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he likes older girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.23,0:00:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long were they going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the end of his 2nd year to the summer of the 3rd.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only half a year? That's short.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.03,0:00:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that long?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:11.99,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,The rumors came out of nowhere and spread like wildfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm having a really hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're well enough to be running in gym again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.37,0:00:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I got a 34 on the last math test!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.75,0:00:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finally free of that zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess next time you'll have to get higher than a 56.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll fail if your average is under 30, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.38,0:00:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll try my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano is still the same as ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:01:03.00,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Usotsuki na anata nakimushi no atashi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:08.96,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite umaku ikanai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.96,0:01:15.09,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshare shita kami mo rain suton no tsume mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:21.06,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata wa kidzuki mo shinai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:28.44,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love kanashii namida nanka ja nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:33.15,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me ga kawaite hirihiri suru dake
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:39.07,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono unmei bakari I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:47.96,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi dake wo atashi dake wo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:52.88,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsui omoi wo uketomete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:02:00.01,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doko made mo tsunagattetai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:06.77,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaikunai nakigao mo se mo aishiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:01:03.00,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't things go well between
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:08.96,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,the liar, you, and the crybaby, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.96,0:01:15.09,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't notice my styled hair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:21.06,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,or my nice set of press-on nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:28.44,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love isn't about the unhappy tears that go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:33.15,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears only leave my eyes dry and hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:39.07,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:47.96,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,between only you and only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:52.88,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to accept your hot feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:02:00.01,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,and be taken by you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:06.77,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite your uncute, tearful face and your shortness, I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:21.74,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,800)\pos(140,384)}Episode 2 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:17.61,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! They don't look alike at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:19.45,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, they really don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:20.95,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Asahi Middle School yearbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:22.95,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto-san's older sister is in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:24.24,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the one Yano was going out with!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, come take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'll... pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, anyone have change for a 5,000 yen bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dooooon't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone have change for 5,000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano just doesn't change...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we met, Yano's just been like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I just don't know anything about him yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:55.19,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:03:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That committee meeting lasted longer than I expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What class was she in again...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class 3-5.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just curious...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must look pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:35.65,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Book: Asahi Middle School Yearbook
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't looked at it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna see?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I didn't want to see it under these circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I don't know what kind of expression to--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:11.18,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx135\fscy190\frz14.353\pos(360,444)}Yamamoto Nana
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He only goes for pretty faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:21.44,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)\fscx136.25\fscy170\frz335.687\pos(561,48)\c&H8C837C&}Surprised
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:21.44,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)\c&H8C837C&\frz24.719\fscx141.25\fscy162.5\pos(293,70)}Surprised
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-She's really pretty, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but this is nothing. In person, she's even prettier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've completely lost to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't really... resemble Yamamoto-san, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one of you fell for the other first?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me. It was love at first sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you started dating right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it took a while. She had a boyfriend at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you steal her away?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, are you trying to make me look bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just never seen Yano so fixated on one thing before...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have loved to brag about her, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was my first. The first I'd ever really loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My chest hurt, but since Yano smiled as he talked, it quickly settled down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I probably didn't want to accept it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The existence of someone Yano loved...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I might like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just ignore me! I just wanted to try sayin--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, wanna go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh? W-Wait a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really like me back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second! You hesitated!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did too! You definitely did!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:05:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that sort of "like".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking if you really, really like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's just forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're going to go out, I want you to like me back...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Okay"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it was the first confession I'd made since I was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to get a quick and painfully honest "okay" as an answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I should've pretended to not hear him and said "yeah"...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were sound asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Can't you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto, show me you can fill in the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, you stay here and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano? Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? You look pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good against anemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so lukewarm and gross...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's leftover from my lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It's not expired or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness... we can still talk normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before, you kept badgering me if I really, really liked you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well... I wouldn't call it "badgering"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were quite the badger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really, really like someone like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to hesitate to answer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you don't just feel the same way I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm pretty hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go get something sweet to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Takeuchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't usually see you around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I get it. Asahi Middle School is around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our haunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that means Yano hangs out here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna take a look inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, he's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make room for two more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl's my class president.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class president?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be pretty smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:08:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Especially in math.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I heard you're in the same class as Yamamoto Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be so dark and annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she's nothing like her older sister, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only is she antisocial, but she's so creepy, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be an inferiority complex or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, those two have always been compared to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything about her. You just judge her by her looks. Quit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? We were in the same class for three years of middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we'd know more about her than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You knew her for three years, but those are the only things you can say about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't even leave messages for people correctly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Motoharu and Nana-san got into a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they hadn't fought...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they would've been together that summer vacation, and what happened would--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not something to talk about here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... s-sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys getting so serious all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive anyone who badmouths Nana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... and about Yamamoto's little sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's... yeah, she's fine just the way she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not as bad as you all say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Takahashi Nana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't homeroom, so quit acting like the class president. It's annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dropped my wallet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:10:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the first girl who's ever told me to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me say some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron! Idiot! Jackass! Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can only see Nana-san in your eyes, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Moron, idiot, jackass", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my mother isn't a bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a prostitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my girlfriend was a cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rea--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was with another guy when she died in the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:11:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was her previous boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were never through with each another...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually don't know if that was really true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I don't really want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if there's one thing I know for sure, it's this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she ever felt that she wanted to see another guy, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it must partially be my fault for making her feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... can't find any words...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm getting a text message.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Where are you and what are you doing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... taking... Takahashi... san... home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... you don't have to take me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to, so why don't we go to a pho--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pho...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we go get our picture taken at photo booth together?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such an idiot, asking at a time like this. Such a total idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't one that takes our whole picture be better?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... not one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really feels like it's been forever since I've been in one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano's... smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, when I think about it... he's always smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, you're really strong, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, a person can't say the sorts of things you just told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to press the "confirm" button!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I thought so. This one's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're like the woman of 1,000 masks! It's hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... I think it's a lot easier to place the blame on yourself than someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Not the other way around?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it easier to blame someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you blame someone else, you'll just get stubborn and say you'll never forgive them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when you blame yourself, you can shrug it off since there's nothing you can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you won't get angry that way, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, I'm not being fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pressed the "confirm" button, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the dork! Look at your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:14.66,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,I look like a guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And not only that... my head's bigger than his.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I look like some octopus alien or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute...? As an octopus...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:15:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, we decided what we'll be doing for the school festival at the last committee meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, due to the large number of classes doing cafés, we weren't able to do one. Instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:59.12,tab.,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&}Sign: What to do for the School Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:08.92,tab.,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\fscx120\fscy156.25\pos(302,107)}Short play
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:10.63,tab.,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(362,104)\fscx47.5\fscy66.25}Short play
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our third choice, a short play, won in the ballot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "our third choice" won?! "Our"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi, were you asleep when we voted?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I suck at rock-paper-scissors...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's a problem. isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you borrow a classroom instead of the auditorium for those...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...only the student judges and teachers will come to see it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just too lame...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured that, so I thought about what I could do to increase the audience...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I came up with the perfect idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:39.12,tab.,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFDFDFD&\fscx105\fscy91.25\pos(254,436)}L\Ne\Na\Nd\N:\N \NY\Na\Nn\No\N\NM\No\Nt\No\Nh\Na\Nr\Nu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:39.12,tab.,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\fscx81.25\fscy137.5\pos(522,226)}(Still not sure what we're\N going to do yet, but...)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll bring them in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll get all the girls here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, I'm gonna decide what play to do today. What do you wanna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me. Do whatever the heck you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You don't have to get so mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I always have to clean up your mess?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clean up my mess...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:15:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I was thinking of being the costume director...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be so nice to always take the easy way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes... you can really be a bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So whenever someone does something inconvenient for you, he's a bastard. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:14.57,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)\an7\fscx106.25\fscy111.25\pos(388,34)\c&HD57DC8&}This is the person who\N confessed her love to \Nhim last week ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just mad about before, aren't you? It's true that I was a little hasty, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't have a good eye for these sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I said before was a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This little...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-When I said I liked you, I was wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Told you so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... just... don't get it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, how should I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do either of you have any stories involving murder?! One that really lets the main character have it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:16:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love stories are out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could kill him! I could just kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:03.92,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like Nana wants to kill Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I'll draw a mustache on this devil! Yes! A mustache!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a student council meeting during lunch tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they'll assign the classrooms for the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that so? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Takeuchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you all got together...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... that's a daily thing for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all have big mouths.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, I heard your class is putting on a play?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's really a pain in the neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks to him, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, that douchebag!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not talk about him. My mouth will rot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must've done something to really annoy you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Sometimes he's so cold, it's hard to believe his blood is flowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't even think of others! He could be a little more sensitive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The complete opposite of you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm really trying my hardest, I get nothing in return...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I feel like that, it really aggravates me to see people like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the worst?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's worse than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... people will still come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of Yano, everyone was cool with the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that type of person, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who brings a soccer ball to recess, so all of the other kids cheer and go to the field to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when that type of person leaves...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...everyone just gets bored and quits playing. The type who really has a strong presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of those types, and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...really...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...admire that part of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:19:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding! If I talk about that moron any more, not only will my mouth rot, but so will my brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you think of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From that day forward, we were really busy looking for a good script...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and we had no idea of the incredible thing that would happen two days later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...? Our... our...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...our class has no classroom for the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a student council meeting during lunch tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they'll assign the classrooms for the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard our class might not be able to put on a play after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?! That doesn't bother me one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard Takahashi forgot to go to the room assignment meeting, so we couldn't get a classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not completely out of a classroom yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still open classrooms in the third building.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The third building? That's totally far away from everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody would come to that run-down building, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't get into this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that girl doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not Nana's fault! I heard the person deciding who goes where forgot about our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana tried her hardest to protest, but she was told it was too late to move things around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't listen to her at all... they said it was her fault for missing the assignment meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When's the meeting today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should've just ended...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think some people will still be around?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine. If anything happens, I'll take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the classroom distribution...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano and I... are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I'm telling you, it's already been decided. Just use one of the leftover rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you the leftovers are no good, so change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:08.53,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano has a different way of thinking than most people...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder when I began getting that feeling from him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he's totally irresponsible, he's serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he cuts corners, he's confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first school building was impossible to get, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep... contradicting yourself, Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought... you weren't going to clean up after my messes anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:22:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I'm just too full of pride, too weak-minded, everyone's "friend"...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have too strong a sense of responsibility, not reliable in the least...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.63,0:22:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and just a timid coward...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all mean someone who's too softhearted!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.47,0:22:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no eye for anything... I confess my love too quickly... I rely on people too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, a...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not trying to put on a comic skit here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.19,0:22:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's so bad, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.94,0:22:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being softhearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.57,0:22:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.99,0:22:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think confessing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was the mistake you're making it out to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.50,0:22:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you always evade the important questions by saying things like "who knows?" or "I dunno"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.85,0:22:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.98,0:22:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can call it irresponsible or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.90,0:23:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can call it whatever you want, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.74,0:23:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't I all right the way I am, not knowing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.74,0:23:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's saying it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's contradicting himself again...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.75,0:23:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... he might just be all right the way he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:05.42,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Koko ni ite itsudemo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.42,0:22:11.22,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Koko ni ite watashi wo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.22,0:22:16.48,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Koko ni ite miteite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:21.65,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono mama zutto
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:24.94,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Te no hira no naka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.94,0:22:27.82,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,afuredashisou na
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:33.62,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata ga kureta "hajimete"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:39.42,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Watashi hitori ja kokoro ga yuretara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:45.72,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Minna koborete shimau
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:53.51,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata no ookina te de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.51,0:22:59.19,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Watashi goto tsukamaeteite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:05.07,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Konna ni mo konna ni mo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.07,0:23:11.24,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Tayorinai watashi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.24,0:23:17.66,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Dakedo ima wa anata no te wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.66,0:23:20.46,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,sukoshi tookute
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:40.90,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Koko ni ite yasashiku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.90,0:23:46.61,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Koko ni ite anata no
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.61,0:23:52.37,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Koko ni ite sono te de
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.37,0:23:55.28,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutsundeite ne
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.08,0:24:03.21,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsumo hitori de aruiteru michi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.21,0:24:07.30,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Hirosugite samishii dake
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.01,0:24:14.76,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Futari de arukeba shiawasena kimochi
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.76,0:24:21.39,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Sore dake de ippai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.15,0:24:28.94,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata ga egao dattara
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.94,0:24:34.62,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Watashi mo onaji de itai
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.62,0:24:40.54,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Sore na no ni sore na no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.54,0:24:46.67,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Watashi dake furuete shimau
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.67,0:24:53.05,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaze yo douka suki no kimochi
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.05,0:24:56.18,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,sotto tsutaete
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:05.42,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Be here... always...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.42,0:22:11.22,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Be here... look...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.22,0:22:16.48,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Be here... at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:21.65,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like this, forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:24.94,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The "first time" you gave me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.94,0:22:27.82,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,seems like it's going
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:33.62,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,to overflow in the palm of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:39.42,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,If my heart wavered alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:45.72,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems like everyone would vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:53.51,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,On that day, you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.51,0:22:59.19,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,took hold of me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:05.07,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,even though, even though
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.07,0:23:11.24,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so unreliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.24,0:23:17.66,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,But you still stretched out your
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.66,0:23:20.46,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,arm and hand to me, just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:40.85,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Be here... with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.85,0:23:46.61,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Be here... gentle hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.61,0:23:52.37,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Be here... of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.37,0:23:55.28,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and embrace me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.08,0:24:03.21,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The path I always walk alone
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.21,0:24:07.30,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,is too wide, and only makes me lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.01,0:24:14.76,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,If we walked together, I'd be filled
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.76,0:24:21.39,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,with happiness, and that'd be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.15,0:24:28.94,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're smiling,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.94,0:24:34.62,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be smiling too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.62,0:24:40.54,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet... yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.54,0:24:46.67,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like I'm the only one who will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.67,0:24:53.05,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wind... please gently tell him
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.05,0:24:56.18,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,of my feelings towards him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.03,0:25:35.06,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HDC6CE3&\c&HFDE2FF&\fscx97.5\fscy122.5\pos(450,377)}Episode 3 Preview...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.44,0:25:09.07,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,They call that\N sort of thing "being blind".
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.07,0:25:11.69,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't really fallen\N in love with anyone before!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.69,0:25:14.32,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,They call those sorts\N of people "immature know-it-alls".
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.32,0:25:17.45,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and really fall in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.45,0:25:18.78,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.78,0:25:22.21,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, there may not be\N anyone left who you really love...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.21,0:25:25.25,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,...and that might be\N a really sad thing for you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.25,0:25:26.96,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm watching you, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.96,0:25:29.55,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always watching you, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.55,0:25:31.30,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always watching over you, so...!
